ctapimkt
------------------------------------------
Library and program to read the german health insurance card (KVK) and the
german electronic health card (eGK) from a certified card reading device on
the serial port in Linux with kernel 2.6.x.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libctapimkt-devel-1.0.1-1bl4
  libctapimkt0-1.0.1-1bl4
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sourceforge.net/projects/ctapi-mkt/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/ctapi-mkt/ctapimkt-1.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack ctapimkt-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./ctapimkt-1.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/ctapimkt-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/ctapimkt-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libctapimkt0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libctapimkt-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(ctapimkt)
  /usr/bin/mkter.exe
  /usr/bin/mktlin.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/ctapimkt.README
  /usr/share/doc/ctapimkt/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/ctapimkt/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/ctapimkt/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/ctapimkt/README

(libctapimkt0)
  /usr/bin/cygctapimkt-0.dll

(libctapimkt-devel)
  /usr/include/ctapi.h
  /usr/lib/libctapimkt.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/ctapimkt.pc

